   <strong>Example 1</strong>
   <br>
   Find the reciprocal of the following numbers (a) 2 (b) <sup>2</sup>&frasl;<sub>3</sub> (c) 0.02 (d) <sup>41</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub>
