    <br>
     $975 is 65% of a sum of money. Calculate the sum of money.
     <br>
     <strong>Solution</strong>
     <br>
     <strong>Let the sum of money = x </strong>
     <br>
     65% of x = $975
     <br>
     100% of x = <sup>100</sup>&frasl;<sub>65</sub>  x 975 = <sup>97500</sup>&frasl;<sub>65</sub>  = $1500
